Class SimpleTimeAdvanceComponent

All Implemented Interfaces:
Component, GenericStateModel
public class SimpleTimeAdvanceComponent
extends BaseServletComponent

This plugin gathers and integrates completion information from nodes in a society to determine the "completion" of the current tasks. This plugin should be included only in one agent at the root of the society such as NCA. When the root determines that completion has been acheived (or is never going to be achieved), it advances the clock with the expectation that the advancement will engender additional activity and waits for the completion of that work.
